<br/>


<img alt="" data-id="475594987" src="https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/10061b000001ab92iF7E8_R_600_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient" width="560"/>
<br/>

快到终点了，耶!
<br/>

快到山脚时有厕所，当时我们看到有厕所心理都有一阵恐惧，怕是大山那种要带走的厕所，还好不是，但很臭，我没去。
<br/>


<img data-id="475517985" src="https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/10071b000001aqctc48A1_R_600_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient"/>
<br/>


<img data-id="475515020" src="https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/10031b000001abdbtA4F7_R_600_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient"/>
<br/>

我们终于下山了！
<br/>

名号登山口一出来就是青年之家，我们在那蹭厕所用了。这里的红叶也很漂亮呢。
<br/>


<img data-id="475515914" src="https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/100q1b000001aaxuv533C_R_600_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient"/>
<br/>


<img data-id="475516311" src="https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/100r1b000001a82ry1B3E_R_600_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient"/>
<br/>


<img data-id="475518756" src="https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/100q1b000001aaxuv533C_R_600_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient"/>
<br/>


<img data-id="475516930" src="https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/100p1b000001a8sm05CD2_R_600_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient"/>
<br/>

开车回去的时候，不小心开错路了，不过经过一个很漂亮的地方呢。
<br/>


<img data-id="475516803" src="https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/10051b000001ac5yz627A_R_600_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient"/>
<br/>


<img data-id="475516692" src="https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/100b1b000001ac1q2CDC9_R_600_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient"/>
<br/>


<img data-id="475517852" src="https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/10021b000001agr10B9D2_R_600_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient"/>
<br/>

回去车上拍的红叶
<br/>


<img alt="" data-id="475594917" src="https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/100p1b000001a9rgs1B05_R_600_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient" width="560"/>
<br/>

开车回去时经过这个草地很漂亮，应该在三瓶山东侧。
<br/>

去到美乡町昨天买菜超市附近的Lawson，我们吃了好些东西，当时实在太饿了。我们吃了oden(日本卤煮），之后洗碗公主使劲推销lawson的炸鸡排，搞到其余三人吃完oden又买了鸡排吃。
<br/>


<img alt="" data-id="475594884" src="https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/100h1b000001ac7ao9B27_R_600_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient" width="560"/>
<br/>

最后六点半去到教会，阿姨们已为了我们准备了丰富的晚餐，有牛肉，海鲜及其他口味的pizza。聚会的时候，大家都趴下来睡觉了.....
<br/>


<img alt="" data-id="475594912" src="https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/100i1b000001a9g6dAE70_R_600_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient" width="560"/>
<br/>

丰富的pizza晚餐。
<br/>

还没完，第二天小x请我们去她家里玩，为我们准备丰盛的晚餐。
<br/>


<img data-id="475516923" src="https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/100q1b000001aay7j4E6D_R_600_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient"/>
<br/>


<img alt="" data-id="475594968" src="https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/100u1b000001aalp80985_R_600_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient" width="560"/>
<br/>


<img alt="" data-id="475594940" src="https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/100o1b000001a9gzt072C_R_600_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient" width="560"/>
<br/>


<img alt="" data-id="475594953" src="https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/100w1b000001agnx93A35_R_600_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient" width="560"/>
<br/>

连续玩了3天，行程完美结束，大家继续回去写论文。两天在自然环境中度过，心情真是很舒坦。
<br/>

v
